      "name": "Riptide Proxy Operator (Kompiuteris)",
      "description": "Operator of the Riptide commercial proxy-as-a-service infrastructure. Developer username 'Kompiuteris' (Lithuanian for 'Computer') identified from exposed Go pprof debug endpoints. Source code distributed via Telegram Desktop. Operates 8-node proxy cluster across US and Canada with co-located credential stuffing tools.",
